    <item>
      <title>Does 502 Bad Gateway Mean You&#39;re Blocked? Truth Behind the Error</title>
      <link>https://peoplealsoask.github.io/does-502-bad-gateway-mean-blocked/</link>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 Apr 2026 06:20:21 &#43;0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://peoplealsoask.github.io/does-502-bad-gateway-mean-blocked/</guid>
      <description>No, a 502 Bad Gateway error does not mean you are blocked. It indicates a communication failure between servers—usually a temporary server-side problem—rather than a client-side block.</description>
